{"tid":2374254,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[侵侵團隊放飛機] 說好的解密「奧巴馬門」呢？","createTime":"2021-01-21T05:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T06:44:00.000Z","uid":321893,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"54069f5f39bfff9f02bf4d604a435d73f1d4f8d3","tid":2374254,"uid":321893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:48:13.000Z","msg":"又話星期二公佈「奧巴馬門」細節，最後無曬影。<br />\n<br />\n唔好誤會，我都認為今次選舉係有舞弊，但係發覺侵侵團隊成日得個講字，成日話有野爆最後又無發生，鮑威爾、朱利阿里、Lin Wood個個都成日話有招又唔見佢出，侵侵夠話會對付Big Tech，而家又對付左去邊？<br />\n<br />\n老實講，好失望。<br />\n我地一直無放棄過，但係無惗到侵侵竟然放棄美國、放棄自己、放棄全世界，由得佢今後墮落。<br />\n<br />\n輸既，都係全世界人。"},{"pid":"a718da4886e0d94977fcfc254ff05605d1e23299","tid":2374254,"uid":321893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:51:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"121b7656dc07c253b10d4b1e96f34e0fd8c4f242","tid":2374254,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:53:48.000Z","msg":"樓主反侵=3毛/pr/分化/放負<br />\n自己揀個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae18ef7cd04f3ec0aed3e8253f30bdcca36c05a","tid":2374254,"uid":321893,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"121b7656dc07c253b10d4b1e96f34e0fd8c4f242","tid":2374254,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:53:48.000Z","msg":"樓主反侵=3毛/pr/分化/放負<br />\n自己揀個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:54:57.000Z","msg":"我係愛侵力"},{"pid":"e35eaadd0f48cd2e27a384e4d90054e4b3e73aa8","tid":2374254,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:55:40.000Z","msg":"郭文貴打飛機唔係中國人專利"},{"pid":"7cb92921c78a8775ac2663ea74eaa6cf8023206f","tid":2374254,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"未抽乾個趙(?)澤....唔可以解密住.....<br />\n(好似係)"}]}